A Studio Ghibli style illustration of a warm, sunlit gathering space where a diverse group of people sit in a loose circle on grassy hills, their body language open and engaged. At the center, a figure with gentle features listens intently to another person, visible threads of soft golden light flowing between the individuals like delicate ribbons connecting their hearts. The scene features rolling emerald hills dotted with wildflowers, puffy cumulus clouds in a watercolor sky, and a magnificent ancient tree with sprawling branches providing dappled shade. Small spirit-like wisps float peacefully among the group, representing unspoken understanding and emotional connection. The color palette is soft and dreamy with warm amber, sage green, and sky blue tones characteristic of Miyazaki's aesthetic.
